{"tid":607651,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Winning 2013巴甲球員討論","createTime":"2018-03-27T12:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T13:34:49.000Z","uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72e394cbaf29263bda27533b63c1b359da54fd78","tid":607651,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T12:47:06.000Z","msg":"如果有玩Winning 2013都知有巴甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴甲球員係master league存在真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多又平又好用又好升嘅人<br />\n<br />\n龍門有Rafael Cabral，艾利臣，Leo Navacchio<br />\n<br />\n後衛馬昆奴斯，Doria，Dede<br />\n<br />\n閘R. Galhardo，Cicinho<br />\n<br />\n中場有卡斯美路，費蘭度 (<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />曼城果位)，Airton，Rodrigo Caio，干素，惠靈頓尼姆，班納特，Wesley，Maylson<br />\n<br />\n前鋒Victor Andrade，Leandro，達美奧，Ademilson<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位巴絲當時有冇大量買入巴甲球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 不要講尼馬，條友係你拎晒冠軍之後轉會成功率都係2%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，串到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再講佢成日俾鍠疤拜買走，身價最少40-50M<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e40ab97a1223dff450e6b5608f2231007ebe85","tid":607651,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"考古game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n18年仲玩緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3873deab40024118d0c91c19cf78484fb5c3609","tid":607651,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09e40ab97a1223dff450e6b5608f2231007ebe85","tid":607651,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"考古game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n18年仲玩緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T12:54:06.000Z","msg":"因為Winning 2013以新一代計真係唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋想玩下柏圖"},{"pid":"7a596e2c636ed61b2e4054b741f47b9b42219de4","tid":607651,"uid":165598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T13:03:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"510d789e569c28b3bf8e45ae310aa8fed54e98c6","tid":607651,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a596e2c636ed61b2e4054b741f47b9b42219de4","tid":607651,"uid":165598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T13:03:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T13:06:05.000Z","msg":"我講下者<br />\n都好耐冇玩"},{"pid":"94414ebf78713eb3d6d2484acf0e13ce0c9656d8","tid":607651,"uid":87120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T13:18:06.000Z","msg":"我只玩 2011 同 2017 <br />\n<br />\n因為要 用 細痲佬 同 碧咸"},{"pid":"3e03554d001f03dd93cfee103d67cfdb440b2938","tid":607651,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94414ebf78713eb3d6d2484acf0e13ce0c9656d8","tid":607651,"uid":87120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T13:18:06.000Z","msg":"我只玩 2011 同 2017 <br />\n<br />\n因為要 用 細痲佬 同 碧咸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T13:34:49.000Z","msg":"2011有碧咸?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知道2010有"}]}